{"tid":831733,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【真正隱世正氣歌神】重有冇人記得 關正傑 Michael Kwan？","createTime":"2018-09-22T08:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T04:32:25.000Z","uid":35221,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51f626080812aa8cd9d6dda8d67539ad037cea69","tid":831733,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/d06713hvt6d_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fd06713hvt6d_496_280%2F0&h=c0147852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與菊姐合照、應該都係合唱緊倆忘煙水裡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141015/large/15ec1p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141015%2Flarge%2F15ec1p12.jpg&h=aa459cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與陳慧嫻合照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141015/large/15ec1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141015%2Flarge%2F15ec1p1.jpg&h=a0050978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2014與妻子於美國之近照<br />\n<br />\n關正傑（Michael Kwan Ching Kit，1949年3月27日－），香港資深歌手兼建築師，活躍於1960年代至1980年代，與「歌神」許冠傑齊名為「雙傑」。1988年正式退出樂壇。<br />\n（中文維基百科）<br />\n<br />\n==<br />\n<br />\nMichael 名曲精選，多數都係武俠、歷史、氣勢強大嘅劇情劇主題曲，或者係一啲非常勵志正面嘅歌，佢正氣形象可謂表露無遺：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n萬水千山縱橫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yLrHKW-Cwj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyLrHKW-Cwj4&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ecd2f49b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yLrHKW-Cwj4</a><br />\n<br />\n天蠶變<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=upt6THj4ry8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dupt6THj4ry8&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b9bec0e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=upt6THj4ry8</a><br />\n<br />\n大地恩情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_GSOWTWWpec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_GSOWTWWpec&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9d36c7b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_GSOWTWWpec</a><br />\n<br />\n[當年學友比賽冠軍出道都係唱大地恩情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e-piAC4cZoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De-piAC4cZoY&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=45838878\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e-piAC4cZoY</a><br />\n<br />\n英雄出少年<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b7HjfZ7tQZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db7HjfZ7tQZQ&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0ce067fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b7HjfZ7tQZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n星<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmR2R4I42Kg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUmR2R4I42Kg&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8f488db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmR2R4I42Kg</a><br />\n<br />\n一點燭光<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EtK62MeLjlY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEtK62MeLjlY&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6deb0ad5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EtK62MeLjlY</a><br />\n<br />\n蚌的啟示（與區瑞強、盧冠廷合唱）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mP_7ID6mWpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmP_7ID6mWpU&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f860a686\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mP_7ID6mWpU</a><br />\n<br />\n天龍訣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=72vEWKBlBkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D72vEWKBlBkE&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2cd9e86f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=72vEWKBlBkE</a><br />\n<br />\n變色龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qD_ii4reyCE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqD_ii4reyCE&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bc204688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qD_ii4reyCE</a><br />\n<br />\n天籟...星河傳說<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=airBYHZ8cSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DairBYHZ8cSw&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=68337301\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=airBYHZ8cSw</a><br />\n<br />\n但同時唱一啲柔情似水、纏綿悱惻嘅歌都非常掂：<br />\n<br />\n漁舟唱晚<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9sdzsE1FDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI9sdzsE1FDI&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e362486a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9sdzsE1FDI</a><br />\n<br />\n雪中情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KqS9IfWmwIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKqS9IfWmwIU&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6b7647b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KqS9IfWmwIU</a><br />\n<br />\n倆忘煙水裡（與關菊英合唱）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7RSUG1zib0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7RSUG1zib0&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2ababf4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7RSUG1zib0</a><br />\n<br />\n人在旅途灑淚時（與雷安娜合唱）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mGIID2mvOBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmGIID2mvOBg&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8d9b7d6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mGIID2mvOBg</a><br />\n<br />\n這個秋天（與鮑慧珊合唱）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PPTLZ9kObIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPPTLZ9kObIU&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=28a828a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PPTLZ9kObIU</a><br />\n<br />\n遲早是一對<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DeP_StVQOc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDeP_StVQOc0&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=742abcf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DeP_StVQOc0</a><br />\n<br />\n佢話移民就移民、退出樂壇非常堅決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連煇哥都叫過佢出山都堅持唔肯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我遺憾出世得太遲，冇機會睇到佢live <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢啲歌對我影響都好深，主要都係嗰堆正氣歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15a9b83c1fa490bdb48deb435999353cd4f6109","tid":831733,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87434d39bdffaedcfa0f599a291e9a702f45d469","tid":831733,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0