mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最後都改返做嗅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d8MboqXhodM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd8MboqXhodM&d=8p5wVFk5uVpaK%2FyZ%2FVU1JQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4dd9656a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d8MboqXhodM</a>"}]}